The pivoting question is: How to better understand your customer. Throughout the course we will use a single database to apply the different concepts and Data Science techniques. Three tools will be presented and used: SQL, Power BI and Microsoft Azure ML If you are a marketer who want to be introduced to the Data-Driven analysis field, then this course is for you.
